#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This guide will introduce you to the many features of the &plasma; workspace "
"and applications and describe many common tasks you can perform."
msgstr ""
"V tem priročniku boste spoznali številne funkcije delovnega prostora in "
"aplikacij &plasma; ter opisali številna običajna opravila, ki jih lahko "
"opravite."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
