"For more information on &kde;, visit the <ulink url=\"https://www.kde.org/"
"\">KDE website</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Za več informacij o &kde; obiščite <ulink url=\"https://www.kde.org/"
"\">Spletno stran KDE</ulink>."

